stories.title: Kaif, Yuvraj Singh see India home
stories.summary: India completed their second victory in two days to go top of the table in the NatWest triangular series, beating Sri Lanka by five wickets with four overs to spare at the AMP Oval

stories.title: India in seemingly unstoppable vein
stories.summary:
CricInfo    
The current Indian team seems to be showing a lot of character and a
real hunger to win
